                      RATAN CAPITAL MANAGEMENT LP
                    

•   NEW YORK, NY
                          • Investment Advisor
                          • Hedge Fund
                      
How do I update this listing?




                                             Ratan Capital Management is based out of New York. Ratan Capital Management is a hedge fund  with  1-10 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $375,459,000 (Form ADV from 2017-03-30).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $208,871,000 in managed 13F securities
